summary:
I am owner of the company Alles in 3D. Here I help you with making your idea come reality. Together we will design your product and produce it on any scale.I am experienced in the software solidworks, making 3D renders, 3D printing, CNC machining and mold making for injection molding. 

Everything is possible at "Alles in 3D". Several companies are already working with me. I developed customised laboratory equipment, parts for machinery or cleaning tools, parts for the car industry or products for the consumer market.

Let me know what your idea is, and we will make it happen.
Check out the website for more information, and the several finsihed projects: www.allesin3d.nl
Or contact me directly via casper@allesin3d.nl
